summary: Email correspondence from August 30, 2019, regarding the transmission of interview notes related to the Epstein case, with an attached scanned document. The email indicates that FBI 302 forms will be prepared from these notes.

events.title: Transmission of Epstein Interview Notes
events.description: An email was sent attaching scanned interview notes, with a note that FBI 302 forms will be prepared from them.

locations: 290 Broadway 9th FL; Joint Bank Robbery T/F
keyFacts: Interview notes related to the Epstein case were transmitted via email on August 30, 2019.
The notes were scanned from a Xerox Multifunction Printer located at 290 Broadway 9th FL, Joint Bank Robbery T/F.
The email indicates that formal FBI 302 reports will be prepared from these interview notes during the following week.
